model.name: Laureate Platform Desert Boot
model.disambiguatingDescription: This version of the Laureate platform desert boot takes inspiration from the vibrant color palette of Louis Vuitton's Cruise 2022 collection. Crafted from a mix of materials, including calf leather and Monogram canvas, it features a distinctive quilted detail at the back. This iconic model is characterized by its treaded platform outsole and long leather laces.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• Green
  • Mix of materials
  • Leather laces
  • Treaded rubber outsole
  • 5 cm / 2-inch platform
  • LV Circle rubber patch on the tongue
  • Vuitton signature on the side
  • Patent Monogram-canvas back loop
  • Made in Italy
